*******************************************************************************
This is a development release and should not be considered stable. If you want
stable use version 0.1.14, please use x11-wm/fluxbox instead.

This is one version of many to come before a stable 1.0.0 release. Check out the
RoadMap on http://fluxbox.sourceforge.net/roadmap.php for more information about
upcoming versions.

ATTENTION: Now, the bsetroot has been renamed to fbsetroot at 0.9.14, be
	   expect for many unoffical themes' background will not working
	   unless you edit in the style for rename bsetroot -> fbsetroot by
	   yourself. Other way can be done is to install the x11-wm/boxtools
	   that has bsetroot if you don't want to edit any theme.
*******************************************************************************
